<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2008-01-31</DATELINE><TITLE>Rodent Diagnostic Testing</TITLE><BODY>Abstract Clinical medicine is an important part of scientific medicine that is all too often neglected when treating rodents and small mammal pets. As with more traditional pets, a progressive diagnostic regimen should include a thorough history, clinical signs, physical examination, and laboratory findings.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>